description:
To reward people getting in early on the Magic Voodoo Dolls, we will keep increasing the price of the Magic Quantum Photographs (the NFTs) a little, step by step. This award is here for everyone who got into our community early but missed the sales. This award will help you to get a little discount on the very last chance to get some of the "Magic Voodoo Dolls - The OG Collection".

The time frame to get this award will end on the Birthday of the Magic Meme God, 4/20.
name: 1st official discount award of the "Magic Voodoo Dolls - The OG Collection"
